headline: Wellness in Every Sip: Yogi® Refreshes Tea Aisle with Bold, New Organic Tea Concentrates
summary: Refreshing, organic and ready to satisfy your taste buds, Yogi®, a trusted leader in purpose-driven organic tea blends, stirs up the tea aisle with the debut of its new Organic Herbal Tea Concentrates. Easy-to-prepare concentrates make refreshing iced tea while delivering the functional wellness benefits Yogi fans love, including immune and digestive support.

headline: U.S. holiday spending set for steepest drop since pandemic, PwC survey shows
summary: PwC, which polled about 4,000 U.S. consumers between June and July, said shoppers on average plan to spend about $1,552 per person, down 5.3% from last year.  The last comparable decline was in 2020, when average spend fell 7.6% to $1,187.
